&lt;li&gt;Establish governance for organizational readiness, change saturation, and adoption planning, providing insights and recommendations to transformation leadership.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Develop stakeholder engagement strategies tailored to global, regional, and functional audiences.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
