&lt;p&gt;The Global Director of Client Partnerships is a senior functional leader responsible for defining and driving the global strategy, structure, and performance of SIE&amp;nbsp;Media Solutions&amp;nbsp;Client Partnership&amp;nbsp;(Sales)&amp;nbsp;organization. This role&amp;nbsp;leads a&amp;nbsp;global&amp;nbsp;team of managers and client partners, scaling the function to deliver sustained revenue growth, strategic partner value, and long-term&amp;nbsp;business&amp;nbsp;impact.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Operating at the intersection of sales and platform strategy, this leader moves beyond individual account ownership to shape portfolio-level direction, establish global frameworks, and influence enterprise-wide partnership and decision-making. The role requires the application of expertise in the PlayStation ecosystem, global advertising markets, and complex commercial partnerships, combined with strong organizational leadership and operational rigor.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
