&lt;p&gt;&lt;em&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Global Strategy &amp;amp; Portfolio Leadership&lt;/strong&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Define and drive the global Client Partnerships strategy, translating SIE Media Solution’s priorities into scalable partner frameworks and multi-year growth plans&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Develop and execute growth strategies that expand SIE Media Solutions’ advertising business with non-endemic brands, with a focus on scaling demand across Programmatic, FAST/CTV, and emerging ad solutions&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Oversee a portfolio of strategic partnerships, ensuring alignment to revenue growth, retention, and broader ecosystem objectives&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Build strategic engagement frameworks with media holding companies and multinational advertisers to accelerate adoption of new commercial offerings and unlock incremental revenue streams&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Identify market trends, client needs, and emerging opportunities to inform long-term commercial strategy and investment decisions&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;em&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Organizational Leadership &amp;amp; Capability Building&lt;/strong&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Lead and develop a global organization of client partners&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Establish team structures, operating models, and performance expectations to enable scale and consistency aligned with existing and new sales models and offerings&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Build organizational capability through talent development, succession planning, and leadership coaching&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
