&lt;p style=&quot;color: !important;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: #000000;&quot;&gt;Reporting to the Senior Manager, Global Content Communications and dotted line to the Manager, LATAM Communications, this individual will support the development and execution of social marketing&amp;nbsp; and communications strategy across key owned PlayStation social media channels in all Latin America Spanish Speaker territories with a particular focus on the Mexico region.&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
