&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Perform in-depth analysis to address key strategic areas in the customer journey, decipher analytical results, and deliver insights using hypothesis testing and experimental design&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
